<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>게시글 수정 - SchoolHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/post-new.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("partials/header", { school: typeof school !== "undefined" ? school : null }) %>
  <main class="container">
    <a href="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts/<%= post.id %>" class="back-link">
      ← 게시글로 돌아가기
    </a>

    <h1>게시글 수정</h1>
    <p>수정한 게시글은 관리자 재승인 후 다시 공개됩니다.</p>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="error-box">
        <%= error %>
      </div>
    <% } %>

    <form class="post-form" action="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts/<%= post.id %>/edit" method="POST">
      <label>
        카테고리
        <select name="category" required>
          <option value="자유" <%= post.category === "자유" ? "selected" : "" %>>자유</option>
          <option value="질문" <%= post.category === "질문" ? "selected" : "" %>>질문</option>
          <option value="건의" <%= post.category === "건의" ? "selected" : "" %>>건의</option>
        </select>
      </label>

      <label>
        제목
        <input type="text" name="title" maxlength="200" value="<%= post.title %>" required />
      </label>

      <label>
        내용
        <textarea name="content" rows="10" required><%= post.content %></textarea>
      </label>

      <label>
        글 비밀번호
        <input type="password" name="password" required />
      </label>

      <button type="submit">수정 요청하기</button>
    </form>
  </main>
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>